ware. After designing, you can export your templates to the best email service providers like Mailchimp, Hubspot, Constant Contact, and others. \n\nOur main goal is to help you create the best-looking emails while saving your time, effort, and money. \n\nStart designing yours for free: https://accounts.unlayer.com/signup?returnUrl=https://console.unlayer.com\u0026plan=free\n\nWant to go a step ahead? Try Unlayer Embed. \n\nYou can customize the appearance of your editor, enable or disable features and enhance security with Unlayer’s Embed. Follow our guide to know more about Embed’s additional features. https://docs.unlayer.com/docs/security\n\n\nFollow us on social media: \n\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/unlayer\n\nLinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/unlayer/?viewAsMember=true\n\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/unlayerapp\n\n#emailbuilder #emaileditor #emailmarketing #emailtemplates #htmlemailtemplates","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2umTbiyK92E/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEiCKgBEF5IWvKriqkDFQgBFQAAAAAYASUAAMhCPQCAokN4AQ==\u0026rs=AOn4CLCjHMQnrEsWjtEWsfIOU3BEt_m2Jw","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2umTbiyK92E/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEiCMQBEG5IWvKriqkDFQgBFQAAAAAYASUAAMhCPQCAokN4AQ==\u0026rs=AOn4CLCgy6M9ibNoExGxL5sDB1lxphBBUQ","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2umTbiyK92E/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCPYBEIoBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=\u0026rs=AOn4CLDv4fLK-kA9Gg6SxvjkR0YWh-iYLw","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2umTbiyK92E/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCNACELwBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=\u0026rs=AOn4CLDM10KLdCq2bxnjez3pcbszy2dWfw","width":336,"height":188},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2umTbiyK92E/maxresdefault.jpg","width":1920,"height":1080}]},"allowRatings":true,"viewCount":"9774","author":"Unlayer","isPrivate":false,"isUnpluggedCorpus":false,"isLiveContent":false},"playerConfig":{"granularVariableSpeedConfig":{"minimumPla